          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Debt-to-GDP Transparency and Stabilization Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires the President's annual budget and congressional budget resolutions to include the ratio of the public debt to the estimated gross domestic product.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
